name: Temple of Horus
description: The Temple of Horus. A Priest meditating with 4 Tools representing the four elements of the Universe. Behind him are two Statues of two Godforms of Horus. The Sign of the Enteror (Ra-Hoor-Khuit) and the Sign of Silence (Harpocrates). If you look into the Entry in the Background you will find the Tree of Life, too.
